Podio,is,an,online,work,platform,It,combines,hundreds,of,specialized,work,apps,with,messaging,tasks,reporting,workflow,and,contact,management,to,let,users,design,a,customized,online,workplace,The,Podio,API,lets,users,integrate,with,other,services,and,build,tools,and,applications,on,top,of,Podio,The,Podio,API,is,RESTful,with,data,returned,as,JSON